  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yeah, I got kicked out of school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my father said, well, that's great.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You-- you can work for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, my mother was not too happy about that, and she decided to get me a job somewhere else because she felt I wouldn't learn anything from my dad.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because whenever I asked my dad something about how do you do this, how do you do that, my father said, you're too young to know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He wouldn't-- he wouldn't give me information or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then she got me a job as an apprentice at a place called Netex, N-E-T-E-X, [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Modelum, ?] which was a manufacturer who made women's jackets and coats.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I literally went through the entire-- I learned everything about the company, even some of the bookkeeping, you might say, and how the company was run.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I didn't get much pay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I think I got $5 a month.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I learned a lot, and it later on helped me a lot in my life when I went to Australia because I claimed I was a cutter.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I got myself a job as a cutter, even though I had only seen it, how the cutting was done.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And later on, I-- I went to school to learn pattern-making and designing, and that helped me when I came to-- to the United States.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't want to stay in Holland for a number of reasons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents were having continuous arguments, and I was sick and tired of their fighting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, look, I'm gonna leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the two of you can have your divorce, and you don't have to worry about me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they were kind of arguing which-- where I should live, with my mother or my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
